	0x3f0, 370
	fd%d

IDE disks
  --disable-ide			block/{cmd640,ide-cd,ide,rz1000,triton}.c
	hd%d	(disks)
	wcd%d	(cdroms)


*** SCSI disks

Disks all show up as `sd%d'.  CD Roms all show up as `cd%d'.  Tapes and
generic are not currently supported.

